{"tid":926890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位巴打絲打唔好再反共產黨","createTime":"2018-12-03T19:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T14:32:34.000Z","uid":202340,"like":60,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f599f7fa4f7cd02a5ed5e6b90d00d451e413a10","tid":926890,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:07:40.000Z","msg":"共產黨好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係共產黨困住班中國人 世界一早玩完了<br />\n依家中國有防火長城 班中國人都會翻牆出嚟搞到成個網絡世界烏煙瘴氣 如果冇咗仲得了<br />\n同埋共產黨限制中國人出外旅行 其實諗深一層係德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....<br />\n所以大家唔好再反共產黨 要對共產黨敬重！ 因為共產黨就好似一條狗帶咁綁住中國呢一隻癲狗......"},{"pid":"5d3e2c41001e7d4c01fc809a2cc5f303e65e1c18","tid":926890,"uid":202340,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:10:57.000Z","msg":"其實共產黨自己都好委屈 日日畀人駡.....<br />\n唔知習近平叔叔有冇成日匿埋喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434fc60656933cd7bcaf0927841d5a458c54f05e","tid":926890,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:17:01.000Z","msg":"希望大家喺下一次反共之前停一停諗一諗<br />\n諗下如果冇咗共產黨香港會點..."},{"pid":"2dab1f3388a56823d6465f27b66c878332a5c2f0","tid":926890,"uid":181021,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"434fc60656933cd7bcaf0927841d5a458c54f05e","tid":926890,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:17:01.000Z","msg":"希望大家喺下一次反共之前停一停諗一諗<br />\n諗下如果冇咗共產黨香港會點..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T19:19:18.000Z","msg":"我淨係知有共產黨  香港就係俾佢箍住個隻狗"},{"pid":"b66441dc2f32dcbe1e1bf34fe09c23630129620a","tid":926890,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"2dab1f3388a56823d6465f27b66c878332a5c2f0","